{
  "uid": "loadgen-federation",
  "title": "Loadgen Federation",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "tags": ["loadgen", "v2", "federation"],
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {"from": "now-30m", "to": "now"},
  "templating": {"list": []},
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Phase 3.9 Dependency Notice",
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Phase 3.9 Federation Scenario Required\n\nThis dashboard depends on metrics produced by the **Phase 3.9 federation scenario**. The following metrics do not exist yet:\n- `loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket` (4 stages: publish→outbox, outbox→inbox, inbox→canonical, canonical→visible)\n- `loadgen_federation_e2e_latency_seconds_bucket` (end-to-end cross-site latency)\n- `loadgen_federation_flap_drain_seconds` (time for a flap event to drain)\n\nAll panels below will show **'No data'** until Phase 3.9 ships."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Stage 1: Publish → Outbox p99",
      "description": "Latency from message publish to outbox stream enqueue. Requires Phase 3.9. Shows 'no data' until §3.9 ships.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 3},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket{stage=\"publish_to_outbox\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket{stage=\"publish_to_outbox\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Stage 2: Outbox → Inbox p99",
      "description": "Latency from outbox stream to remote inbox stream (cross-site transfer). Requires Phase 3.9. Shows 'no data' until §3.9 ships.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 3},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket{stage=\"outbox_to_inbox\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket{stage=\"outbox_to_inbox\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Stage 3: Inbox → Canonical p99",
      "description": "Latency from inbox stream to canonical message stream (inbox-worker processing). Requires Phase 3.9. Shows 'no data' until §3.9 ships.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 11},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket{stage=\"inbox_to_canonical\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket{stage=\"inbox_to_canonical\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Stage 4: Canonical → Visible p99",
      "description": "Latency from canonical stream to message being visible to subscribers. Requires Phase 3.9. Shows 'no data' until §3.9 ships.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 11},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket{stage=\"canonical_to_visible\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_stage_latency_seconds_bucket{stage=\"canonical_to_visible\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "E2E federation latency (stacked stages) + flap drain",
      "description": "End-to-end cross-site latency (sum of all 4 stages) and flap drain time. Requires Phase 3.9. Shows 'no data' until §3.9 ships.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 19},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "stacking": {"mode": "normal"}}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_e2e_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "e2e p99",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_e2e_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "e2e p50",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(loadgen_federation_flap_drain_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "flap drain p99",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
